Account name: On Cloud Canine LLC | Fear Free Certified Professionals
Description:
Why Day Training is a Game-Changer for Your Dog’s Mental Health!

Did you know that dogs, just like us, need mental stimulation to stay happy and healthy? Day training at daycare isn’t just about learning commands — it’s about keeping their minds sharp, reducing anxiety, and boosting confidence! 🧘‍♂️💡

Here’s why it’s a must:
1. Prevents Boredom 💤: Mental stimulation is key to avoiding destructive behaviors.
2. Improves Focus 🎯: Helps your dog stay calm and focused throughout the day.
3. Reduces Stress & Anxiety 😌: Structured learning gives your pup a sense of purpose and confidence.
4. Stronger Bond with You ❤️: The skills they learn create a better connection between you and your dog!

Give your dog the mental workout they deserve! 🐕💪 

#OnCloudCanine #CloudCanineCrew #DogTraining #MentalWellBeing #HappyPup #DogDaycare #SmartDog #PuppyLove #DogLife #TrainToGain #PositiveReinforcement #FearFreeCertified

Account name: On Cloud Canine LLC | Fear Free Certified Professionals
Description:
Alyssa is working on building a relationship with our resident Nervous Nelly; Esther. If you’ve been following us for awhile, you know Esther was adopted last summer and her pawrents have put in a great deal of work to help her feel comfortable and increase her socialization. 

Whenever we introduce new staff to her, it’s a weeks to months long process to ensure she’s comfortable and we’re going at her pace. Today, she surprised us by eating out of Alyssa’s hand within the first 15 minutes! 

Calming body language and positive reinforcement go a long way! Great job, Alyssa & Esther! 👏🏻

Account name: On Cloud Canine LLC | Fear Free Certified Professionals
Description:
We’re excited to announce some delicious new additions to our lunch menu that are sure to make your furry friends wag their tails! Introducing our Seasonal Barkuterie Board and Pumpkin Pupsicle!

🍽️ Barkuterie Board: Imagine a charcuterie board designed just for dogs! Our Barkuterie Board is a colorful assortment of tasty, pup-friendly delights, including:
* Cheeses like cottage cheese with a sweet addition of honey
* Savory Meats like freeze-dried lamb liver cubes
* Yummy Veggies like bite-sized bell peppers and butternut squash
* Fruity Treats like a serving of applesauce with a cinnamon garnish
* Delicious Dairy such as plain greek yogurt or goats’ milk blended with pumpkin and frozen to delight your pups taste buds

🍂 Pumpkin Pupsicle: Cool off this fall with our refreshing Pumpkin Pupsicle! Made with pureed pumpkin, carrots, and plain greek yogurt, these frozen treats are not only delicious but also packed with nutrients. Perfect for a warm day or as a special treat after playtime!

Both of these options are made with love and care, ensuring they’re safe and nutritious for your furry companions. We can’t wait for your pups to dig in!

When are they available? Starting Wednesday, October 2nd, the Barkuterie Board and Pumpkin Pupsicle will be available every day during lunch. Be sure to sign your pup up for a treat they’ll love!

#oncloudcanine #oncloudcaninecrew #dogdaycare #doggydaycare #fearfreepets #akronohio #barkuterie #pupsicle
